  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/eb50d03140d27385fb5180eb1472d6fc.poster.avif?t=1722673630\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/eb50d03140d27385fb5180eb1472d6fc.webm?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/eb50d03140d27385fb5180eb1472d6fc.mp4?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Let's workout with a girl!<br>Are you ready for the first-ever workout/rhythm game?<br>This is a VR-only game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/cb1a8d2f67cd2685f7271aebce2d3e40.poster.avif?t=1722673630\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/cb1a8d2f67cd2685f7271aebce2d3e40.webm?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/cb1a8d2f67cd2685f7271aebce2d3e40.mp4?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Workout x Rhythm Game</h2><br>Move the \"lock-on circle\" and<br>aim the targets along the music!<br>Press the correct buttons to help her work out!<br><br>Arrow Targets: Choose the right direction!<br>Number Targets: Tap them multiple times!<br>Long Targets: Press and hold!<br>Wide variety of targets await you!<br><br>Unwind with easy and fun gameplay!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/9b4029dab0814cfd1e4678be92542f0b.poster.avif?t=1722673630\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/9b4029dab0814cfd1e4678be92542f0b.webm?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/9b4029dab0814cfd1e4678be92542f0b.mp4?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sanae Sanada</h2><br>She is a bookworm from Kamakura, Japan.<br>You used to play with her when you were a child, but it has been a while.<br>One day, she asks you, a personal trainer to help her workout.<br><br>She is not an athletic type. You wonder what changed her mind......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/38922613b2c2523d824706d5078b94ad.poster.avif?t=1722673630\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/38922613b2c2523d824706d5078b94ad.webm?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/38922613b2c2523d824706d5078b94ad.mp4?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wide Variety of Mini Games</h2><br>Clean windows, sort through documents, and play games with her......<br>A variety of mini games will help you to learn more about each other.<br><br>Moreover, the workout will get more effective by finishing the mini games!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/eb50d03140d27385fb5180eb1472d6fc.poster.avif?t=1722673630\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/eb50d03140d27385fb5180eb1472d6fc.webm?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/eb50d03140d27385fb5180eb1472d6fc.mp4?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Let's workout with a girl!<br>Are you ready for the first-ever workout/rhythm game?<br>This is a VR-only game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/cb1a8d2f67cd2685f7271aebce2d3e40.poster.avif?t=1722673630\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/cb1a8d2f67cd2685f7271aebce2d3e40.webm?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/cb1a8d2f67cd2685f7271aebce2d3e40.mp4?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Workout x Rhythm Game</h2><br>Move the \"lock-on circle\" and<br>aim the targets along the music!<br>Press the correct buttons to help her work out!<br><br>Arrow Targets: Choose the right direction!<br>Number Targets: Tap them multiple times!<br>Long Targets: Press and hold!<br>Wide variety of targets await you!<br><br>Unwind with easy and fun gameplay!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/9b4029dab0814cfd1e4678be92542f0b.poster.avif?t=1722673630\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/9b4029dab0814cfd1e4678be92542f0b.webm?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/9b4029dab0814cfd1e4678be92542f0b.mp4?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Sanae Sanada</h2><br>She is a bookworm from Kamakura, Japan.<br>You used to play with her when you were a child, but it has been a while.<br>One day, she asks you, a personal trainer to help her workout.<br><br>She is not an athletic type. You wonder what changed her mind......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/38922613b2c2523d824706d5078b94ad.poster.avif?t=1722673630\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/38922613b2c2523d824706d5078b94ad.webm?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2778440/extras/38922613b2c2523d824706d5078b94ad.mp4?t=1722673630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wide Variety of Mini Games</h2><br>Clean windows, sort through documents, and play games with her......<br>A variety of mini games will help you to learn more about each other.<br><br>Moreover, the workout will get more effective by finishing the mini games!",
